<record_update table="sys_report">
    <sys_report action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE">
        <aggregate>COUNT</aggregate>
        <aggregation_source/>
        <chart_size>medium</chart_size>
        <description>Manager View dashboard bar widget data source. Aggregates ALL records in x_casemgmt_case grouped by the priority Choice field with COUNT(*) per bucket. Four bars expected (Low, Medium, High, Critical) when seed data spans all priority tiers. UNFILTERED by design - shows the entire team backlog distribution across the urgency tiers including terminal-state cases, enabling managers to assess whether the team is over-indexed on Critical/High volume (signals operational stress) or whether Low/Medium cases dominate (signals normal intake mix). Replaces ArkCase's CaseFile.priority + Pentaho aggregation pipeline with a native GlideAggregate-backed sys_report. Different aggregation than x_casemgmt_all_cases_by_status (group by status) and x_casemgmt_all_cases_by_type (group by type); same Manager View dashboard audience per AAP Section 0.4.4. Same chart type as x_casemgmt_all_cases_by_status (bar) but lower-cardinality grouping (4 ordinal urgency tiers vs. 6 lifecycle stages); ordinal urgency tiers benefit from left-to-right linear ordering inherent to bar charts.</description>
        <field_list/>
        <filter/>
        <format/>
        <group_by>priority</group_by>
        <is_real_time>false</is_real_time>
